WEBVTT

00:00:15.359 --> 00:00:15.800
Boss.

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:17.359
Someone jumped from the 2nd-floor window!

00:00:19.280 --> 00:00:21.120
Listen, this is a big deal.

00:00:21.879 --> 00:00:23.120
Keep your phone on you at all times.

00:00:24.120 --> 00:00:24.920
I'm off.

00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:06.760
Bro Mao.

00:01:06.959 --> 00:01:08.000
Bro Mao, you're here.

00:01:17.719 --> 00:01:18.959
Bro... Bro Mao, wait a sec.

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:40.359
Bro Mao.

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:46.960
Dad, there's a spider!

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:48.240
What's wrong, Paopao?

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:49.719
There's a spider over there.

00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:52.039
Where?

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:53.800
Alright, alright, alright.

00:02:54.039 --> 00:02:54.919
It's gone, it's gone.

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:56.439
All gone, all gone.

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:58.520
Come here.

00:02:59.039 --> 00:02:59.960
You got so scared.

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:06.680
Tell Dad, how big was that spider?

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:11.199
The spider was this big!

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:13.000
That big, huh?

00:03:18.479 --> 00:03:21.759
Mom says you only like winning cases.

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:26.840
Yeah.

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:29.000
Dad...

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:31.599
Dad really wants to win.

00:03:33.039 --> 00:03:33.719
But...

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:36.639
Dad never gets the cases he wants.

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:40.080
Same with me.

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:42.719
For this school singing contest,

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:44.479
I didn't get picked.

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.599
We'll just keep trying, then.

00:04:00.199 --> 00:04:01.319
Do you know how to fold it?

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:03.000
Of course.

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:05.560
Didn't I teach you how?

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:08.360
Get some sleep now, okay?

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:10.000
We have another full day of fun tomorrow.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:13.280
Dad's right here with you.

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:14.960
Okay, the spider won't come back.

00:08:51.759 --> 00:08:52.320
Let's go.

00:09:17.279 --> 00:09:18.600
We still haven't found Chen Yongjiang.

00:09:18.759 --> 00:09:19.960
We've been to Chen Yongjiang's house.

00:09:20.159 --> 00:09:21.039
Only his wife was there.

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:21.879
She claimed she didn't know a thing.

00:09:21.879 --> 00:09:23.759
Management said they separated years ago.

00:09:24.039 --> 00:09:24.960
At the time of the incident,

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:26.799
No sign of Chen Yongjiang either.

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:27.759
So...

00:09:27.799 --> 00:09:29.240
where was he last seen?

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:30.240
We checked the security cameras.

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:32.240
At 10:15 AM on the day of the incident,

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:33.320
right outside Feng Mao Company.

00:09:33.399 --> 00:09:34.360
And he never came back out.

00:09:34.559 --> 00:09:35.399
I checked all the surveillance

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:36.720
from the streets near Feng Mao Company.

00:09:36.799 --> 00:09:37.360
Nothing.

00:09:38.799 --> 00:09:39.320
Alright then.

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:41.000
Let's check the people who came and went

00:09:41.039 --> 00:09:42.000
between his last appearance

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.279
and our arrival at Feng Mao Company.

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:44.720
And check the vehicles too, alright?

00:09:47.559 --> 00:09:49.440
You veterans really know your stuff.

00:09:51.159 --> 00:09:52.519
Is that supposed to be a compliment?

00:10:13.879 --> 00:10:15.320
Dad, Dad, come over here!

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.679
Look over there, it's so pretty!

00:10:20.879 --> 00:10:22.759
The sea is so deep here!

00:10:23.799 --> 00:10:24.919
See the seabirds?

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:29.039
They're off to catch fish.

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:48.759
In Xin Qili's bathroom,

00:10:48.919 --> 00:10:50.240
we found mixed DNA samples.

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:52.399
A match confirms it's Chen Yongjiang's.

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:53.440
Also,

00:10:53.679 --> 00:10:54.799
on the night of the incident,

00:10:54.879 --> 00:10:56.519
the neighborhood cameras did catch

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:57.639
footage of Chen Yongjiang.

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:58.799
Fast-track the approval process.

00:10:59.000 --> 00:10:59.879
Request the tech department

00:10:59.879 --> 00:11:01.360
to track Chen Yongjiang's phone

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.039
and vehicle.

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:02.480
Got it.

00:11:02.519 --> 00:11:03.600
Alert every checkpoint.

00:11:03.679 --> 00:11:05.039
If spotted at any airport or station,

00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:05.639
arrest him on sight.

00:11:05.639 --> 00:11:06.519
Yes, sir.

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:08.559
Look at this...

00:11:08.639 --> 00:11:09.399
Brother-in-law.

00:11:14.919 --> 00:11:16.080
What brings you here?

00:11:18.279 --> 00:11:19.759
You have to work, and so do I.

00:11:20.440 --> 00:11:21.200
Feng Mao Company...

00:11:22.159 --> 00:11:23.159
What exactly is this case?

00:11:23.919 --> 00:11:24.919
Don't pull that with me.

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:26.679
This case is extremely serious.

00:11:26.919 --> 00:11:27.559
But let me tell you,

00:11:27.559 --> 00:11:28.759
it's a dismemberment case.

00:11:29.080 --> 00:11:31.320
The only link to the victim that day

00:11:31.320 --> 00:11:32.919
is Feng Mao Company's fleet of vehicles,

00:11:33.519 --> 00:11:34.919
including yours.

00:11:35.480 --> 00:11:36.759
Everyone involved

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:38.039
will be brought in for questioning.

00:11:38.679 --> 00:11:39.399
No problem.

00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:41.799
You just had to go on that exact day.

00:11:41.879 --> 00:11:43.320
I swear, I can't believe you.

00:11:46.519 --> 00:11:47.720
Come over for dinner sometime.

00:12:03.720 --> 00:12:05.559
Lawyer Luo.

00:12:10.360 --> 00:12:12.000
Where've you been?

00:12:13.840 --> 00:12:14.399
You...

00:12:14.799 --> 00:12:15.600
What are you doing?

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:20.159
There are cameras here!

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:24.600
Did we hit you, curse at you,

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.879
or do anything to you?

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:38.159
Where did Bro Mao go?

00:12:41.559 --> 00:12:42.600
Where's Bro Mao?

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.519
You think you deserve to know?

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:51.120
Is Bro Mao hiding

00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:53.600
where he stashes his things?

00:13:07.559 --> 00:13:09.200
This is really the first time I've seen

00:13:10.039 --> 00:13:11.759
a dog working for a cat.

00:13:15.879 --> 00:13:17.480
If you hear anything about Bro Mao,

00:13:18.559 --> 00:13:20.120
you know what to do, right?